thread.title: NICOLA STURGEON SAYS MAJORITY IN PARLIAMENT FAVOURS CUSTOMS UNION MEMBERSHIP

title: NICOLA STURGEON SAYS MAJORITY IN PARLIAMENT FAVOURS CUSTOMS UNION MEMBERSHIP
text:
MAJORITY IN PARLIAMENT FAVOURS CUSTOMS UNION MEMBERSHIP 3:55pm EDT - 00:31
At 2018 Nicola Sturgeon says that she believes there is a majority in the UK Parliament that is in favour of remaining part of the European Union customs union.
